Text: OUTRO INESQUECIVEL, EXCELENTE PLEAS DONT STOP.....YOU ARE THE BEST..

Animal Instinct sounds AMAZING!!!!! The drums are incredible. You managed to get amazingly rich full sound out of these. The soundtracks were some of my first Elvis records, so while many people hate them, I really love them. Thank you for these uploads! To quote "Wisdom of the Ages"  "....to such a man, I bow"
